steps.name: I am an CFA user and Lands on shop page
add Accessories to basket within limit in details page and navigate to basket
I Land on the Non Phone related basket page and choose home delivery option
input TEST and ACCEPTA and other valid details in Delivery page and Click on the 'Continue button'
land on the Non Credit check payment page and input TEST ACCEPTA and other details and click 'Continue on next step'
Continue to Review page and review the order
Verify contents of order confirmation page for Accessories containing In Stock
